Package: prefio
Title: Structures for Preference Data
Description: Convenient structures for creating, sourcing, reading,
        writing and manipulating ordinal preference data. Methods for
        writing to/from PrefLib formats. See Nicholas Mattei and Toby
        Walsh "PrefLib: A Library of Preference Data" (2013)
        <doi:10.1007/978-3-642-41575-3_20>.
